  <div class="trac-ticket-buttons">
  </div>
    <div class="comment searchable">
      <p>
I think this is a false positive of the CSRF protection. It happens because the CSRF token is rotated on login.<br />
</p>
<p>
It was likely discussed on the mailing list or in another ticket before but I don't remember the outcome.<br />
</p>

    </div>

