  <div class="trac-ticket-buttons">
  </div>
    <div class="comment searchable">
      <p>
This happens to my users pretty frequently for whatever reason (possibly the back button is involved). Reloading the POST request doesn't fix it, because it will re-POST the old csrf token. The user needs to press back, reload (GET) the page, and then re-submit the form.<br />
</p>

